Version 2.4.136

- AbstractView.java (bounds()): New function that returns the bounding
  rectangle of a View. Option to decrease the internal padding.
- AbstractView.java (force()): Function to force layout of a View chain.
- CAndroidSliderView.java (_internal_actionEnd()): Tunning the method
  'fling()' of Scroller class to take a little less time to end.
- CAndroidSliderView.java: Changed Scroller to OverScroller so we can choose
  the interpolator animation function. Solves the problem of slowlyness.
- CAndroidPagerView.java: Changed Scroller to OverScroller so we can choose
  the interpolator and twick the paging animation.
